    <h1 class="headline-lg">The Digitalancers<br>Platform</h1>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Payxem is one platform with two core products for every digital professional: <strong>Payments</strong> (invoices and pay links at app.payxem.com) and <strong>Portfolio</strong> ({username}.payxem.com). One signup, one link, one brand.
    </p>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top: 12px;">
      We launched in April 2026 to solve a problem thousands of freelancers know too well: getting paid internationally should not require $150 minimum withdrawals or $30 annual fees, and your professional presence should not be scattered across five different tools.
    </p>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top: 16px;">
      If you're a freelancer, consultant, or small business owner in Pakistan, Bangladesh, or similar markets where PayPal does not operate, you've probably dealt with at least one of these:
    </p>
