<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
      <h2>The Important Part</h2>
      <p class="emphasis">We don't hold your money.</p>
      <p>Payxem is software for invoicing, payment coordination, and professional presence. We partner with regulated payment processors to handle the actual money movement, you get the platform that ties your payments and portfolio together under one brand.</p>
      <p>All payments flow through regulated, secure infrastructure. Stripe, PayPal, and our crypto partners are licensed and trusted by millions of businesses worldwide.</p>
      <p>Payxem coordinates the process. We are not a bank, not a payment processor, not a money service. We are the software layer that makes professional invoicing and portfolio hosting accessible to everyone.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

